    "description": "Big on flavour and rich in goodness, this steak dinner hits all the right notes. Serve with sweet potato mash, loaded with black beans, coriander and spring onion then drizzle over homemade salsa macha and dig in. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
